data.description: New 2022 4 bedroom 2 bath home, 1820 square feet on 3 acres in the country. Situated between Rexburg and Ririe off the Archer Highway. Home is tucked off the road for privacy and farm views. Vaulted ceilings, Stainless steel appliances, private primary bedroom suite with double sinks and a walk in closet. Remote controlled blinds. ADT security sytstem, and extra space for an office, playroom or storage. Everything is on one level making accessibility a breeze. Property includes a Shed, trampoline, chicken coop and some fencing. Great location for horses, a hobby farm, or gardening. No covenants allow endless possibilities! Easy to see!
